<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-text
        font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
        color="#475467"
        line-height="140%"
      />
      <mj-image align="center" padding="0" fluid-on-mobile="true" />
    </mj-attributes>

    <mj-style inline="inline">
      /* Ajustes responsivos */
      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .responsive-text {
          font-size: 15px !important;
          padding: 0 10px !important;
        }
        .responsive-title {
          font-size: 22px !important;
        }
        .responsive-signature img {
          width: 120px !important;
        }
        .responsive-logo img {
          width: 160px !important;
        }
      }
    </mj-style>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body background-color="#f5f5f5">
    <!-- Imagem de topo -->
    <mj-section padding="0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          src="https://faexhub.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/portugal/emails/boas-vindas.png"
          width="600px"
          alt="Imagem de topo"
          fluid-on-mobile="true"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="20px 0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          align="left"
          font-size="26px"
          font-weight="bold"
          color="#475467"
          padding="0 50px 10px 50px"
          css-class="responsive-title"
        >
          Olá, <span style="color: #834781; font-size: 26px">{{ nome }}</span>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text
          css-class="responsive-text"
          font-size="19px"
          align="left"
          color="#475467"
          line-height="140%"
          padding="0 50px 10px 50px"
        >
          Obrigado por se cadastrar na Faex Hub. Sua decisão aproxima você dos
          alunos que permanecem firmes mesmo diante dos desafios da tecnologia
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text
          css-class="responsive-text"
          font-size="17px"
          align="left"
          color="#475467"
          line-height="160%"
          padding="0 70px 10px 70px"
          background-color="#F9FAFB"
        >
          <strong>A partir de agora, você poderá:</strong>
          <table
            role="presentation"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="border: none; margin-top: 10px"
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                width="32"
                style="padding-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="26"
                  height="26"
                  viewBox="0 0 64 64"
                  fill="none"
                >
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="32" fill="#78DEAB" />
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="25" fill="#35C67A" />
                  <circle
                    cx="32"
                    cy="32"
                    r="17"
                    stroke="white"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    fill="none"
                  />
                  <path
                    d="M24 32L29 37L40 26"
                    stroke="white"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  />
                </svg>
              </td>
              <td
                style="
                  vertical-align: middle;
                  font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                  font-size: 17px;
                  color: #475467;
                  padding-bottom: 8px;
                "
              >
                Acompanhar nossas novidades e campanhas
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                width="32"
                style="padding-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="26"
                  height="26"
                  viewBox="0 0 64 64"
                  fill="none"
                >
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="32" fill="#78DEAB" />
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="25" fill="#35C67A" />
                  <circle
                    cx="32"
                    cy="32"
                    r="17"
                    stroke="white"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    fill="none"
                  />
                  <path
                    d="M24 32L29 37L40 26"
                    stroke="white"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  />
                </svg>
              </td>
              <td
                style="
                  vertical-align: middle;
                  font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                  font-size: 17px;
                  color: #475467;
                  padding-bottom: 8px;
                "
              >
                Conhecer histórias de fé e esperança
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                width="32"
                style="padding-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="26"
                  height="26"
                  viewBox="0 0 64 64"
                  fill="none"
                >
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="32" fill="#78DEAB" />
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="25" fill="#35C67A" />
                  <circle
                    cx="32"
                    cy="32"
                    r="17"
                    stroke="white"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    fill="none"
                  />
                  <path
                    d="M24 32L29 37L40 26"
                    stroke="white"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                  />
                </svg>
              </td>
              <td
                style="
                  vertical-align: middle;
                  font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                  font-size: 17px;
                  color: #475467;
                  padding-bottom: 8px;
                "
              >
                Contribuir e transformar vidas
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text
          css-class="responsive-text"
          font-size="18px"
          align="left"
          color="#475467"
          line-height="140%"
          padding="0 50px 10px 50px"
        >
          Para finalizar seu cadastro e ter acesso aos recursos exclusivos,
          <strong>confirme sua conta no botão abaixo</strong>:
        </mj-text>

        <mj-button
          href="#"
          background-color="#834781"
          color="#ffffff"
          font-size="17px"
          font-weight="bold"
          padding="10px 0 0 0"
          border-radius="8px"
          width="300px"
          align="center"
          text-transform="uppercase"
        >
          <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px">
            CONFIRMAR CONTA
          </span>
        </mj-button>

        <mj-text
          css-class="responsive-text"
          font-size="12px"
          align="center"
          color="#475467"
          line-height="140%"
          padding="0 50px 10px 50px"
          padding-top="5px"
        >
          Esse link é valido para 7 dias.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-image
          src="https://faexhub.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/portugal/emails/logo.png"
          alt="Logotipo Faex Hub"
          width="200px"
          fluid-on-mobile="true"
          padding-top="20px"
          css-class="responsive-logo"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
